The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence and falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves the use of multiple benchmark datasets, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves the use of loss functions, which is a popular technique in neural networks and falls under the category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
